{"tid":1647470,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有冇人想再黎多次過百萬人既遊行?","createTime":"2019-10-11T18:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T19:07:49.000Z","uid":89923,"like":15,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea8f4a7076ac2316b491ef998f7bfe63fe2b056","tid":1647470,"uid":89923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:18:31.000Z","msg":"見到個10月日程表有感而發, 其實咁早已經plan晒成個十月日程真係好事? <br />\n<br />\n除左7月1同10月1, 每次做得好睇既抗爭都係早一星期左右通知咁我地先聚到人, 同警察鬥突發我地好難贏, 人地用電話用walkie通知, 我地靠論壇同telegram邊夠人快?<br />\n<br />\n以後唔該一日集中一個時間一兩個地方集合, 勇武自己組隊後可以全港自由行動<br />\n<br />\n好想黎多次百萬人以上既遊行, 俾我知道香港人仲未放棄"},{"pid":"1f00cefc451e6ab543da8241d3d196ba574b3601","tid":1647470,"uid":89923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c29db21121b42d7114441ffc238be923597428","tid":1647470,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:19:19.000Z","msg":"遊行要keep著  遊擊亦要"},{"pid":"adbf808be4767460dcd4ad54044bd5caa92353fe","tid":1647470,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:19:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"333585fd7a3fce049827a21c4a30bbf0d0bcc447","tid":1647470,"uid":89923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56bb1ce587d292c6e5e25dd601c497d3685a1fe","tid":1647470,"uid":89923,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:20:43.000Z","msg":"好想再睇航拍靚相"},{"pid":"cbdea86715ba54f90faa5f0057b959b690086a1f","tid":1647470,"uid":139840,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:21:37.000Z","msg":"上星期已經拉左好多人 兩區遊行真係危"},{"pid":"8e20a33fc1893eb8e79c53ff23cc124242d08e2f","tid":1647470,"uid":89923,"lik